{
  "stem": "6924.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was from those papers, we saw that things are turning around.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think that was-- gave us some hope, that the Germans are not doing so good in Russia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Over the lines, where the Germans were writing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it gave us a little bit of encouragement that maybe, maybe, the day'll come.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then-- then the Russians are going to come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But in June-- [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I would say ?] in May, in May, 1944, we started to hear artillery.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we-- and he was telling us that it must be already the Russians are approaching our-- our place.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that lasted, maybe, about-- the artillery-- maybe four, six weeks, until finally, the Russians started to move, and they occupied the city of [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he came in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He said, we are free to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We are our [? all. ?] And that's how we got liberated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we walked out from that hole-- couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We just couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were very weak because we couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "During staying in that place, at night, we used to go up, you know, get out and move a little bit.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was also-- we had a change, and it was not often.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we walked out, and we hardly couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- but we were happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we decided to go to town, to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, my-- my hearing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With my hearing, that was when I was in that-- in that-- in the first day with the German occupied [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was in that ravine where the-- between the dead people and the-- in the jail.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And when the Germans were throwing hand grenade, and a hand grenade exploded near my-- near my ear.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And from that, and then my hearing was damaged.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A nerve was damaged.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
